{
  "stem": "16473.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I would whine and I would cry and they would make me feel like it was very inappropriate.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the only time I could be with my mother was at night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But of course, she was exhausted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so there wasn't very much time for me in that, in that kind of setting, and I think it affected me very much.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Doing-- in the hotel doing the-- either he was a bellhop or he was an elevator operator.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know he worked in a hotel in some kind of a menial job.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know, except he came up to see the plays.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I suppose my mother had days off, but I don't recall that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was in that area called Margitsziget-- Margaret Island.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very pretty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would imagine they were Jewish, but I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could find [LAUGHS] out, but I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think until I was-- I'm not sure of this-- but I think until I was around four years old.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father got an apartment in Buda and we lived-- and we lived there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know that it was prior to the war, I know I went to first grade, you know, in Hungary living in that building.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, you come in and on your left, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SOBBING] there was a room that was supposed to be my room.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At first, they rented that to somebody to get extra money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was my room and it's not really made for a child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just-- it was a room with built-in bed and built-in cupboards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then if you went a little further straight, then there was the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
